    "en": {
      "title": "Bomb blast in a Canadian bank - 2 dead",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two suspects have been killed in a bomb blast near a bank in British Columbia, Canada.",
        "Six police officers were shot dead at the clash and the police have also taken steps to remove the houses near the nearby houses.",
        "Police in the area have beefed up security, and Canadian police say they are investigating."
